&lt;h1 id="music-recommendation-algorithms-are-unfair-to-female-artists-but-we-can-change-that">Music recommendation algorithms are unfair to female artists, but we can change that.&lt;/h1>
&lt;figure id="figure-algorithms-help-lots-of-people-discover-new-musicimagehttpspixabaycomphotosadult-music-listening-sound-woman-3086302-by-omar-medina-filmshttpspixabaycomusersomarmedinafilms-818453utm_sourcelink-attributionutm_mediumreferralutm_campaignimageutm_content3086302-from-pixabayhttpspixabaycomutm_sourcelink-attributionutm_mediumreferralutm_campaignimageutm_content3086302">
