&lt;p>Have a look at my &lt;a href="https://www.tualumni.at/2019/11/mag-di-dr-christine-bauer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TU Wien alumni profile&lt;/a> (sorry, in German only), where I also provide some supporting words to young talent.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Panelist at VUT Indie Days Köln 2020</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-12-18-panelist-at-vut-indie-days/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2019 17:18:36 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-12-18-panelist-at-vut-indie-days/</guid><description>&lt;p>I am happy to announce that I will join one of the panels at &lt;a href="https://www.vut.de/vut-indie-days/aktuelles-indie-days/artikel/details/vut-indie-days-koeln/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VUT Indie Days Köln&lt;/a>, taking place for the first time as part of the &lt;a href="https://c-o-pop.de/convention/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">c/o pop Convention 2020&lt;/a>. I am looking forward to this event already now.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Watch my PrivacyWeek talk at Relive</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-10-27-watch-my-privacyweek-talk-at-relive/</link><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2019 22:21:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-10-27-watch-my-privacyweek-talk-at-relive/</guid><description>&lt;p>See my PrivacyWeek talk on &lt;a href="https://fahrplan.privacyweek.at/pw19/talk/BYXCVR/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sag mir, was du hörst&amp;mdash;und ich sage dir, wer du bist&lt;/a> at &lt;a href="https://streaming.media.ccc.de/pw19/relive/245" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Relive&lt;/a> until it will be archived on the &lt;a href="https://media.ccc.de/c/pw19" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Media Site of the Chaos Computer Club Germany&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>My talk at PrivacyWeek 2019 is scheduled for Sun, 27 October</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-09-18-my-talk-at-privacyweek-2019-is-scheduled-for-sun-27-october/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2019 14:53:50 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-09-18-my-talk-at-privacyweek-2019-is-scheduled-for-sun-27-october/</guid><description>&lt;p>The program of &lt;a href="https://privacyweek.at" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PrivacyWeek 2019&lt;/a> is online!&lt;br>
My talk with the title &lt;a href="https://cfp.privacyweek.at/pw19/talk/BYXCVR/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sag mir, was du hörst&amp;mdash;und ich sage dir, wer du bist!&lt;/a> (in German) is scheduled for Sunday, 27 October 2019, 15:00&amp;ndash;15:45 in room &amp;lsquo;&amp;lsquo;Saal 1&amp;rsquo;&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Hope to see you there!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Additional talk at AIxMusic Festival on Sunday, 8 September</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-08-27-additional-talk-at-aixmusic-festival-on-sun-8-september/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2019 22:13:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-08-27-additional-talk-at-aixmusic-festival-on-sun-8-september/</guid><description>&lt;p>Besides holding a workshop on the festival&amp;rsquo;s second day (Friday), I will give a talk on &amp;lsquo;&amp;lsquo;Music Information Retrieval: Inside and Outside the Music&amp;rsquo;&amp;rsquo;; together with &lt;a href="https://www.ifs.tuwien.ac.at/~knees/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peter Knees&lt;/a> at the &lt;a href="https://ars.electronica.art/outofthebox/en/aixmusic-day-matinee/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AIxMusic Matinée&lt;/a> on Sunday, 8 September 2019.&lt;br>
Note, the talk is announced with the title &amp;lsquo;&amp;lsquo;Music Information &amp;amp; Music Data&amp;rsquo;&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Workshop at AIxMusic Festival in scope of the 2019 Ars Electronica Festival</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-08-27-workshop-at-aixmusic/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2019 21:41:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-08-27-workshop-at-aixmusic/</guid><description>&lt;p>I happily announce that I will hold a workshop with the title &lt;a href="https://ars.electronica.art/outofthebox/en/aixmusic-tools/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Recommenders and Intelligent Tools in Music Creation: Why, Why Not, and How?&lt;/a> at &lt;a href="https://ars.electronica.art/outofthebox/en/aixmusic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AIxMusic Festival&lt;/a> in scope of the &lt;a href="https://ars.electronica.art/outofthebox/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2019 Ars Electronica Festival&lt;/a>&amp;mdash;together with my co-speakers &lt;a href="https://www.ifs.tuwien.ac.at/~knees/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peter Knees&lt;/a>, &lt;a href="https://www.ifs.tuwien.ac.at/~vogl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Richard Vogl&lt;/a>, and &lt;a href="https://asdfg.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hansi Raber&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>We had some nice media presence lately</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-08-we-had-some-nice-media-presence-recently/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2019 08:19:58 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-08-we-had-some-nice-media-presence-recently/</guid><description>&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s great to see our scientific results being communicated to the public. Our results were well received on the media.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>And here we go, the list of articles on the media:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>22 June 2019, Vorarlberger Nachrichten. &lt;a href="https://epaper.vn.at/kultur/2019/06/21/laenderunterschiede-im-musikgeschmack.vn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Länderunterschiede im Musikgeschmack&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>21 June 2019, studium.at. &lt;a href="https://www.studium.at/linzer-forscher-zeigen-grosse-laenderunterschiede-im-musikgeschmack" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Linzer Forscher zeigen große Länderunterschiede im Musikgeschmack auf&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>21 June 2019, futurezone. &lt;a href="https://futurezone.at/science/linzer-forscher-analysieren-musikgeschmack-in-verschieden-laendern/400529719" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Linzer Forscher analysieren Musikgeschmack in verschieden Ländern&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>21 June 2019, APA. &lt;a href="https://science.apa.at/site/natur_und_technik/detail?key=SCI_20190621_SCI39351351649172790" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Linzer Forscher zeigen große Länderunterschiede im Musikgeschmack auf&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>21 June 2019, Wiener Zeitung. &lt;a href="https://www.wienerzeitung.at/nachrichten/kultur/pop-rock-jazz/2015013-Musikgeschmaecker-und-Watschen.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Musikgeschmäcker und Watschen&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;li>21 June 2019, DER STANDARD. &lt;a href="https://www.derstandard.at/story/2000105229715/linzer-forscher-zeigen-laenderunterschiede-im-musikgeschmack-auf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Linzer Forscher zeigen Länderunterschiede im Musikgeschmack auf&lt;/a> (in German).&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>And, well, also read the original &lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0217389" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PLOS ONE article (open access) on music preferences in 47 countries with respect to what is considered mainstream including recommendation approaches considering users&amp;rsquo; mainstreaminess&lt;/a> by &lt;a href="https://www.mschedl.eu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markus Schedl&lt;/a> and me.&lt;/p>
